{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762434997,"sessionID":"ses_126b3c392ffeqmVxmFv45c0QTG","part":{"id":"prt_ed951274c0016wceRH4SB455UR","messageID":"msg_ed95103700012qrQf7nBygRUrG","sessionID":"ses_126b3c392ffeqmVxmFv45c0QTG","type":"text","text":"One concrete delete-safety issue is emerging: `memory_delete` accepts both `id` and `specFolder` and prioritizes `id`, which can bypass the caller's intended folder scope. Checking schema to confirm whether the handler is the only guard.","time":{"start":1781762434893,"end":1781762434995},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_063db7c95737646a016a338982dc68819182c56b1f7218fc5a","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781762435492,"sessionID":"ses_126b3c392ffeqmVxmFv45c0QTG","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_goqrOfurL178KxKXFamSmbiW","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"memory_delete|DeleteArgs|specFolder.*id|id.*specFolder","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server","include":"*.ts"},"output":"Found 100 matches (more matches available)\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/context-server.ts:\n  Line 251:   'memory_delete',\n\n  Line 1080:     if (typeof validatedArgs.specFolder === 'string' && validatedArgs.specFolder) {\n\n  Line 1081:       recordMetricEvent({ kind: 'spec_folder_change', specFolder: validatedArgs.specFolder as string });\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/memory-crud-types.ts:\n  Line 9: /** Arguments for the memory_delete handler. */\n\n  Line 13: // Feature catalog: Single and folder delete (memory_delete)\n\n  Line 16: interface DeleteArgs {\n\n  Line 119:   DeleteArgs,\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/memory-bulk-delete.ts:\n  Line 32: interface BulkDeleteArgs {\n\n  Line 77: async function handleMemoryBulkDelete(args: BulkDeleteArgs): Promise<MCPResponse> {\n\n  Line 117:     throw new Error(`Bulk delete of \"${tier}\" tier requires specFolder scope for safety. Use memory_delete for individual deletions.`);\n\n  Line 271:           restoreContext: { memoryId: memory.id, tier, specFolder: memory.spec_folder, checkpointName },\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/handlers/memory-crud.ts:\n  Line 29: const handle_memory_delete = handleMemoryDelete;\n\n  Line 36:   handle_memory_delete,\n\n\n/Users/